title: Market share of leading insurance companies in Belgium 2015 to 2018
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 18 different Insurance Companys on X-axis for 4 groups 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Insurance Company AG Insurance had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 4 groups, and it was for 2016. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Insurance Company Foyer for 2015.
Among all the Insurance Companys, 2017 had the highest SOME LABEL in Insurance Company AXA and lowest SOME LABEL in Insurance Company Delta Lloyd.
The maximum SOME LABEL for 2017 that was found in Insurance Company AXA was 0 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL observed in Insurance Company Delta Lloyd.
